      "html": "## You said the problem had affected your health \r\n\r\n[Contact your local council](/local-council-detail) if you're not able to continue living in your home because it's making you unwell. They may be able to help arrange emergency housing.  Make sure you keep sick notes and hospital reports. \r\n\r\nYou can find out more about [what to do if your health has been affected](/health).",
