      "_id": "page.what-to-do-now--content--32",
      "_type": "content",
      "html": "## You said the problem was urgent \r\n\r\n[Contact your local council](/local-council-detail) immediately if the problem is urgent. \r\n\r\n### Emergency court orders \r\n\r\nYou could apply for an emergency court order to fix an urgent problem. However, you should seek professional legal advice before starting an application. You can get information on finding a solicitor and other sources of legal help in [useful resources](/future-resources).   \r\n\r\nYou can also find out more about [what to do if your landlord won't do repairs](https://england.shelter.org.uk/housing_advice/repairs/legal_action_if_your_landlord_wont_do_repairs) on the Shelter website. ",
      "show": {
        "0": {
