      "_type": "content",
      "html": "## You need to contact your landlord or letting agent in writing \r\n\r\nEven if you have already told your landlord about the problem over the phone, by text message or in person, you need to tell them again in writing. This can be by email or letter. \r\n\r\n[Find out more about writing to your landlord](writing-to-landlord).",
