      "_type": "content",
      "html": "## Not paying rent can make the problem worse \r\n\r\nYour landlord may have reason to evict you if you stop paying rent. You can find out more about [withholding rent because repairs haven't been done](https://www.citizensadvice.org.uk/housing/repairs-in-rented-housing/repairs-what-are-your-options-if-you-are-a-social-housing-tenant/withholding-rent-because-repairs-havent-been-done/) on the Citizens Advice website. ",
