      "_id": "page.what-to-do-now--content",
      "_type": "content",
      "html": "## Know your rights and your landlord's responsibilities \r\n\r\nCheck whether your landlord or letting agent is responsible for the problem you told us about in [your rights and your landlord's responsibilities](/rights-responsibilities).   "
    },
